---
title: Marinated Mozzarella Farro Bowl with Roasted Veggies and Pesto
description: Summer in a hearty vegetarian bowl. Creamy mozzarella gets packed with flavour in an herby pesto marinade. Chewy farro adds a wholesome base to arugula, roasted cherry tomatoes and tender zucchini.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bol-de-farro-et-de-mozzarella-marinee-a152f21e.jpg
